###############################################################################
# OBJECTIVE
###############################################################################
Optimize Tracking screen loading performance. Eliminate multiple long loading periods
and interface freezing after vehicle selection.

###############################################################################
# REQUIREMENTS
###############################################################################
requirements:
  - Analyze current loading sequence and identify bottlenecks
  - Reference old iOS implementation for optimization patterns
  - Implement progressive data loading (show map first, then data)
  - Use trackingThrottler from lib/api-throttler.ts
  - Add proper loading states without blocking UI
  - Implement data caching to prevent redundant requests
  - Use async cleanup to cancel pending requests on unmount
  - Show toast notifications instead of full-screen loaders

###############################################################################
# DELIVERABLES
###############################################################################
out: [Optimized Tracking screen with fast loading]
done:
  - Loading time reduced significantly
  - No interface freezing during data load
  - Progressive loading implemented
  - Toast notifications used for feedback
ref: @navitrack-apps/src-client/CODE_MAP.md (TrackingActionScreen, api-throttler).
